u,v:\;\mathbb{R}\to\mathbb{R}
X
\mathbb{R}
\mathbb{E}[u(X)]\mathbb{E}[v(X)]\leq\mathbb{E}[u(X)v(X)]
\mathbb{E}\Big[\big(u(X)-u(Y)\big)\big(v(X)-v(Y)\big)\Big]\geq0 
\iff \mathbb{E}\big[u(X)v(X)\big]+\mathbb{E}\big[u(Y)v(Y)\big]-\mathbb{E}\big[u(X)\big]\mathbb{E}\big[v(Y)\big]-\mathbb{E}\big[u(Y)\big]\mathbb{E}\big[v(X)\big]\geq 0
\iff2\mathbb{E}\big[u(X)v(X)\big]-2\mathbb{E}\big[u(X)]\mathbb{E}\big[v(X)\big]\geq 0
X\geq Y
[X\gt Y]
[X=Y]
[X\lt Y]
